    <!-- About -->
    <string name="title_about">ℹ️ About</string>
    <string name="about_desc">NoteNestX is a fast and simple offline note-taking app designed for everyday use.\n\nCreate, edit, and manage your notes easily without any internet connection.\n\nThe app includes powerful features like Favorites and History, allowing you to quickly access important notes and revisit your recent activity.\n\nBuilt with simplicity, speed, and usability in mind.</string>
    <string name="about_features_title">Features</string>
    <string name="about_features">• Create and edit notes quickly\n• Mark important notes as favorites\n• Access recently used notes with History\n• Offline storage — no internet needed\n• Clean and minimal UI\n• Lightweight and smooth performance</string>

